<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 17:12:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>施纳贝尔表示，欧洲央行对稳定币的最佳反应是数字欧元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-01/best-ecb-response-to-stablecoins-is-digital-euro-schnabel-says</link><description>执行委员会成员伊莎贝尔·施纳贝尔表示，稳定币对金融稳定和货币政策构成了许多风险，欧洲央行的最佳应对措施是确保公共资金仍然是该系统的支柱。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iKefa6MWRRWQ/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2026 00:10:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-01/best-ecb-response-to-stablecoins-is-digital-euro-schnabel-says</guid></item><item><title>美联储沃勒表示稳定币将扩大美国政策的影响范围</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-31/fed-s-waller-says-stablecoins-will-broaden-reach-of-us-policy</link><description>美联储理事克里斯托弗·沃勒表示，稳定币在全球范围内的传播可能会放大美国央行政策的影响力。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ieFSm_UgktQw/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 13:29:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-31/fed-s-waller-says-stablecoins-will-broaden-reach-of-us-policy</guid></item></channel></rss>